data.description: IMPROVED PRICING! BRING AN OFFER! WELCOME TO THIS LOVELY AND SPACIOUS HOME CENTRALLY LOCATED! R.V. PARKING! NO HOA! LOW TAXES! SOLAR PANELS! GREAT curb appeal, Inviting front porch, nice Sized driveway with R.V. Parking! Step through the Double-Door front entry into a Spacious floorplan. There is Decorative tile flooring, an attractive wooden staircase, high ceilings, inviting colors, formal living room, separate formal dining room, and REAL Hardwood flooring. The interior set of double doors leads to a Large Office/Bedroom, and down the hallway is a full Bathroom on the first level. The Sizable Kitchen has a Center Island, granite counter tops, walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, lots of extra storage space/cabinetry, and is open to HUGE family room! There is plenty of natural lighting, real hardwood flooring, and an inviting fireplace encased in tile. Upstairs offers 3 Large Bedrooms, Another Full Bathroom in hallway, a Very spacious Loft with lovely Mountain views and Primary Suite. The Primary Bathroom offers a Jetted tub, nice walk-in closet, dual vanity sink, and tile flooring. The backyard has concrete patio, pergola, grass, mature trees, shrubs, large side-yard and R.V. parking. There is a new solar system as well for electrical efficiency! Inquire for more information.   Community has NO HOA, LOW taxes, is close to parks, schools, and shopping.
